"""Accept the Height of a Person & Categorize as Taller, Dwarf & Average
Problem Description
This problem accepts the height of a person as input and categorizes as taller, dwarf & average."""

height=float(input("Enter the height of a person in cm:"))
if height<150:
    print("Person is dwarf")
elif height>=150 and height<=180:
    print("Person is average")
else:
    print("Person is taller")

output:
Enter the height of a person in cm:145
Person is dwarf
